The micro brewery - Wilmslow:

Always a great experience in this pub and the choose of beer and pork scratching/nibbles are huge. The recently new menu was very tasty. data.text:
The best pub in Handforth. It is traditional and has character. The landlord and landlady are lovely, always say hello, the bar staff are polite and always helpful.
Every Saturday there is excellent themed entertainment, with local community coming together for charity events.
Overall an excellent pub. Definitely recommend
